Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Discretionary
Industry: Distributors - Discretionary
Sub-Industry: Consumer Elec & Applc Whslrs
Jive Communications, Inc was founded in 2006. The company's line of business includes the wholesale distribution of electronic parts and electronic communications equipment.




