Overview of Jive Hosted VoIPUpdated: Jul 23, 2017Jive Hosted VoIP OverviewJive’s voice service is compatible with SIP-based hardware from leading manufacturers, including Polycom, VTech, Yealink, Panasonic, and Cisco. Jive’s hosted services run on Jive Cloud, Jive’s service delivery platform based on open standards. The Jive Cloud architecture was purpose-built to deliver the most reliable, powerful, and economical hosted communication service. 
Jive Voice—our cloud-based phone system—gives you a professional boost. Enjoy our suite of Hosted VoIP features, including unlimited voicemail boxes, auto attendants, and local and long-distance calling. Focus on your priorities, not your tech. Phone system cost too much? Get the Jive upgrade: the latest communications technology for a dramatically lower total cost of ownership. Forget about maintenance costs and software updates. Jive maintains and updates everything for you. It’s the last communications platform you’ll ever have to buy.
